OL,3,GHighlands & Eilean Siar
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FShowers,
OL,6,Fheavy at first over Caithness and
OL,7,FSutherland, will die out this evening.
OL,8,FThen dry with clear spells and turning
OL,9,Frather chilly in places. Thickening
OL,10,Fcloud will bring rain to the south
OL,11,Flater in the night.
OL,12,
OL,13,CThursday:FA cloudy morning with rain
OL,14,Fspreading to all parts. Turning drier
OL,15,Fin the afternoon with a few showers in
OL,16,Fthe west. Some afternoon brightness
OL,17,Fdeveloping around Inverness and Nairn.
OL,18,FWarm.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
