OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FMainly
OL,6,Fdry and warm in the east on Friday but
OL,7,Fcloudier with patchy rain in the west.
OL,8,FMostly dry, warm and bright over the
OL,9,Fweekend.
